STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Porfirio A. NUNEZ-MOSQUEA, Defendant-Petitioner. C-612 September Term 2017
080003 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 9, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002594-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
